				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Re: Are Erudite Evil?<BR>
<BR>
Snobbish as said above. . . now for that evil bit.<BR>
<BR>
Those who worship Solusek Ro (The Burning Prince) will notice when they start and read their character description, it will say things like:<BR>
<BR>
You feel that the others around you are just toys to be used and power is everything.  The world is won by power<BR>
<BR>
etc. . . so a Solusek Ro worshipping Erudite, or any other race that worships him (also Innoluk (sp?) and the other dark gods) could be considered evil by the good folk out there.<BR>
<BR>
Although I don't mind one second being the evil Erudite Wizard I am, watching a few people die infront of me from a mob that they thought could kill &quot;Oh, sorry, I was out of mana&quot; <BR>
<BR>
btw I'm not a jerk, I just role play one =)<BR>
-Paragoth (Brothers of Fire)<BR>
Wizard of Bertoxxulous, Worshipper of the mighty Solusek Ro who shall burn all who oppose him =)
