			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				RE:Good/Evil<BR>
If, on the character select screen (with the rotating portrait), the background is like that of a light temple, then you are good.  If it is dark, like in a cave with lava, then you are evil.  You will notice that certain classes (with the same race) are good and evil.  Try making a new human and change the class he/she is.  The background will change.<BR>
My 2pp
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
