			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				  Greetings dark brothers and sisters of Paineel.  I am Obsydia, human shadow knight of Bertoxxulous, and master of avoiding unnecessary confrontations with the fairer infidel religions.  When a necromancer travels to Qeynos, jump off the boat before you reach the dock and swim under the dock.  There, you will find an underwater entrance into my home, the Sewers of Qeynos.  You are welcome here, as are all of Bertoxxulous' followers.  Feel your way around and you can even find another passage that will lead you to a hole in the wall in North Qeynos, outside the city gates!  From there, be careful to avoid the Qeynos Hills Guards (except Cheslin, kill him at level 4 or 5) and head through the Karanas into Eastern Karana and Beholder by level 14 or so.  At lower levels, (6-10) group in Blackburrow to kill gnolls.  You can hunt in Western Karana at around level 7 or so and the Corrupt Guards will never even notice you are there.  I hope this helps you my brethren and sisters.  Spread the disease of the Plaguebringer!<BR>
<BR>
Obsydia Blackheart <BR>
35th level Shadow Knight<BR>

